title: DWTS's Hannah Brown sports $110 RE/DONE T-shirt to rehearse the foxtrot for Disney Night
text:
Dancing with the Stars contestant Hannah Brown sported a $110 RE/DONE 'The Classic Empowered Women' T-shirt as she headed to rehearsals for the 28th season of the ABC competition in LA on Wednesday.

The 25-year-old Bachelorette 15 alum paired her casual white top with grey sweatpants, matching hoodie, and white sneakers.

The former interior designer was prepping her princess-themed foxtrot with dance partner Alan Bersten for the Disney Night episode airing next Monday.

Last week, Team AlanbamaHannah's beastly paso doble to Icona Pop's 2012 song I Love It featuring Charli XCX scored them 32 points (8, 8, 8, 8).

Before the show, Hannah and the 25-year-old DWTS: Juniors champ let off steam in the Rage Underground 'anger room' where she smashed bottles and screamed: 'These are all my ex-boyfriends!'

'There were multiple bottles because there were multiple guys,' the Tuscaloosa-born beauty admitted to ET on Monday.

At that, Bersten cracked: 'There actually weren't enough bottles.'

Brown dumped her fiancé Jed Wyatt five weeks after his guitar-strumming TV proposal after she discovered he'd been dating singer Haley Stevens in the four months leading up to the taping.

Minnesota-born Alan previously partnered with influencer Alexis Ren (4th place), ice skater Mirai Nagasu (4th place), and singer Debbie Gibson (12th place).

For her turn on The Bachelorette, Hannah is also up for the competition contestant of 2019 trophy at the 45th People's Choice Awards, which air November 10 on E!

Brown competes against former flame Tyler Cameron, The Bachelor's Colton Underwood, RuPaul's Drag Race star Vanessa Vanjie Mateo, The Amazing Race's Tyler Oakley, The Masked Singer's T-Pain, and more.

Also at the rehearsal studio on Wednesday was Dawson's Creek alum James Van Der Beek, who rehearsed his Disney-themed paso doble with dance partner Emma Slater.

Fifth Harmony alum Ally Brooke flashed a big smile at rehearsal in her Flashdance-inspired grey off-the-shoulder top.

The 26-year-old Higher singer headed inside to prep her Disney-themed contemporary number alongside partner Sasha Farber.
